            <div class="comment_body">
                                                                                                                
                Just out of curiosity, my mother has an aversion to using brine when cooking turkey. Is there a way to make the bird delicious without using the sweet elixir?            </div>
            
            <div class="comment_bottom">
                <div class="comment_buttons">
                	                    
